    <item>
      <title>巴西航空公司计划破产，最大贷款方阿布拉将收购巴西航空公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/gol-linhas-plans-bankruptcy-exit-as-top-lender-abra-to-buy-brazilian-airline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Gol Linhas Aereas Inteligentes SA 已达成一项全面重组协议，其最大债权人 Abra Group Ltd. 将接管这家巴西廉价航空公司，并使该公司明年摆脱破产保护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/gol-linhas-plans-bankruptcy-exit-as-top-lender-abra-to-buy-brazilian-airline</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 15:20:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选引发赤字担忧 市政债券价格暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/muni-bonds-tumble-after-trump-victory-ignites-deficit-worries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三早盘，在选民选举唐纳德·特朗普为美国总统后，市政债券暴跌。此前，美国国债暴跌，人们担心特朗普的政策将扩大本已膨胀的预算赤字并导致通胀飙升，导致美国国债遭到抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/muni-bonds-tumble-after-trump-victory-ignites-deficit-worries</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 15:07:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
