    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选对美国企业有利，信贷风险下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/credit-markets-send-some-of-their-most-bullish-signals-in-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国总统大选后，全球信贷市场出现反弹，表明投资者支持预期的减税政策，并且对这场被广泛认为基本打成平手的选举结果感到宽慰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/credit-markets-send-some-of-their-most-bullish-signals-in-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:47:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税风险冲击欧元、德国汽车股；可再生能源下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/european-stock-futures-drop-over-tariff-worries-as-trump-leads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普的选举胜利加剧了人们对征收进口关税的担忧，欧元创下了四年多以来的最大单日跌幅，而汽车制造商等股票表现不佳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/european-stock-futures-drop-over-tariff-worries-as-trump-leads</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:44:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选提振美元 大宗商品下跌 贸易局势紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走强以及唐纳德·特朗普担任总统期间可能出现的贸易争端将削弱原材料在全球市场上的吸引力，大宗商品价格普遍下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选，标普 500 指数创历史新高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市创下历史新高，债券收益率飙升，美元出现自 2020 年以来的最大涨幅，投资者关注唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫以及他的政策对市场的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:05:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>退市风险迫在眉睫，超微股价因前景疲弱而下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/super-micro-slips-on-sales-outlook-that-falls-short-of-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[超微电脑公司 (Super Micro Computer Inc.) 股价周三暴跌，此前这家服务器制造商发布了令人失望的销售预测，且未能公布提交上一财年官方财务报表的时间表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/super-micro-slips-on-sales-outlook-that-falls-short-of-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 21:35:49 GMT</pubDate>
